	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">I agree with what alot of people have said.<br />
<br />
Especially with BoT and Omens and LDoN, all those areas where there are potentially nice upgrades that are droppable, become the really big issues.<br />
<br />
If the items are no drop there is no fuss, because no one will roll on a no drop item if they don't need it.  But there are always those people who will roll on something not needed for their main just to sell later on.<br />
<br />
I don't join pick up groups for many reasons, this being one of them.<br />
<br />
As Alba stated, clarify loot rules before the first mob is pulled so no one can complain later.  People will try some of the silliest things on others if they think they can get away with it. )</font></p>
	
